== Urugezi ==
urugezi n'igishanga giherereye mu [[Akarere ka Burera|Karere ka Burera]] muntara y'[[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|Amajyaruguru]] ni igishanga gifite ubuso

bungana na Hegitare 124 mumyaka yo hambere abaturiye igishanga cya Rugezi bari barakigabije mubikorwa

byinyungu zabo<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/ibidukikije/ibungabunga/article/abatarumvaga-impamvu-babuzwa-gukorera-mu-gishanga-cy-urugezi-ubu-bamaze-kubona-inyungu-zabyo</ref>

== Akamaro k'igishanga cya Rugezi ==
iki [[Umugezi|gishanga cya Rugezi]] nikimwe  mubyanya bikomye kandi gifitiye igihugu ndetse nabaturage bagituriye

akamaro kuko ari indiri yurusobe rw'[[Ibinyabuzima n'inyamaswa byo mu Rwanda|ibinyabuzima]] nkazimwe munyoni,[[Imisambi ya Uganda|Imisambi]],incencebere nibindi 

binyabuzima bitandukanye.<ref>https://www.ikigega.rw/index.php?id=10&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=85&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=8dbc6ff1b6234d12106cc3279e18e559</ref>

ikigishanga kandi kizwiho kuba ari isoko yamazi atanga amashanyarazi kurugomero rwa Ntaruka<ref>https://ar.umuseke.rw/amafoto-tujyanye-gusura-inyoni-mu-gishanga-cyurugezi.hmtl</ref>

=== Aho giherereye ===
Igishanga cya Rugezi gikora kumirenge myinshi itandukanye yo [[Akarere ka Burera|mukarere kaburera]] harimo nka Butaro,Rusarabuye,Rwerere

Kivuye,Gatebe,Ruhunde, nindi yo [[Akarere ka Gicumbi|Mukarere ka Gicumbi]] ariyo Nyankenke, na Miyove.<ref>https://www.ikigega.rw/index.php?id=10&tx_news_pi1%5Bnews%5D=85&tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=8dbc6ff1b6234d12106cc3279e18e559</ref>

